{"tid":2094810,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"施迪安：我沒看出美斯有甚麼不開心","createTime":"2020-07-05T03:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T10:41:57.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5adcd9d810db888ea6795541bf4c0401143237d1","tid":2094810,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:45:45.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿主教練施迪安（Quique Setien）稱，他沒覺得美斯（Lionel Messi）有甚麼不開心，訓練中的一切都很正常。<br />\n<br />\n  有報導稱美斯不想和巴塞續約，打算在2021年夏天離開球隊。對此，施迪安說：「關於這件事，我沒有從美斯那裡聽到甚麼，沒有甚麼變化，我的工作不是去猜測。」<br />\n<br />\n  「我看到他在球會和訓練中很開心，我看到他和以往完全一樣。在必須的時候，我們會坐下來談。」"},{"pid":"c424f3f7cf88d9fe91986a103dc4f3f507a7d131","tid":2094810,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T08:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/heroes-and-villians/images/4/42/5a1c06fce1f081.1557470415117862369255.png/revision/latest?cb=20190318045933\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fheroes-and-villians%2Fimages%2F4%2F42%2F5a1c06fce1f081.1557470415117862369255.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20190318045933&h=510b4168&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eaed1ac781bb7a01d09e6959c3b5c6f82609cfe7","tid":2094810,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"其實美斯係咪俾人關愛慣左，咁受保護有咩唔開心，佢見識過乜野係難受未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6f18735cfd54a2601055763868aeff3eaa9832","tid":2094810,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:41:57.000Z","msg":"呢幾場睇直播都見到佢灰啦，已經回緊塘身邊仲要冇人幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}